title: Interesting Yasuo and Aatrox interaction
body: When Yasuo Knockup (3rd Q) and Aatrox  Dark Flight hit minions at the same time to minions are launched towards the Yasuo who casted his 3rd Q

replies.body:
Hey there,

If you believe this to be a bug then your thread would be better suited for the [Report a Bug](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) board over on NA, before posting there please take a look at the [How to report a game bug](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report/3mQGBEjA-how-to-report-a-game-bug) thread for information on good posting practices while reporting bugs.
